data.title: College of Applied Arts and Technology
data.meta_description: Welcome to Cambrian College, the largest college in northeastern Ontario, serving more than 5,000 full-time and part-time students from approximately 70 countries.L
data.text:
College isn’t just about books, assignments and exams. It’s also about making new friends, having fun, and creating memories that will last a lifetime. To make your Cambrian experience the best it can be, take advantage of our free student services anytime, and join in on student events, workshops, and initiatives that take place during the school year. Helping you succeed in your education and ensuring you’re enjoying college life from the moment you arrive is our top priority!

Start gaining the highest level of skills at Cambrian now – and you’ll be ready to take advantage of the many career opportunities waiting for you just around the corner. The future is yours!
